{"tid":1182498,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"亞視成最後撤離天安門港媒","createTime":"2019-06-02T08:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T09:06:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0f5dafc50ba78418db2a5def5cbbd98f9c246d0","tid":1182498,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190602/20693251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693251&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJIxlCv%2FutJLQSKuuf3SGwDjg%3D&h=30fb76b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190602%2F20693251&h=22152488\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190602/20693251</a><br />\n<br />\n亞視成最後撤離天安門港媒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190602/large/02ed9p8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190602%2Flarge%2F02ed9p8.jpg&h=1666ab35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n軍隊在北京鎮壓後，亞視新聞部是最後撤離的香港記者。電視圖片<br />\n<br />\n在現今很難相信免費電視媒體會支援「六四」，但在八九年「六四屠城」後，市民因悼念北京死難者全港罷工罷課，無綫竟表示不反對同事遊行及罷工。時任無綫高層馮美基還稱，公司決不計較損失支持罷工，主席邵逸夫亦即與採訪六四的記者見面，並說：「我對六四好傷心、好痛心。」前新聞部主管黃應士憶述，當時六叔曾給他一個手提箱，裏面放滿一叠叠共60萬元鈔票，供新聞部採訪之用。<br />\n<br />\n至於亞視，軍隊在北京鎮壓後，新聞部更作即場報道，是最後撤離的香港記者。亞視眾藝員則由亞姐利智帶頭，自發在廣播道總台募捐，又上街由廣播道行去聯合道公園，甚至上酒樓向市民勸捐，支援北京學生。之後亞視藝人再自發舉行橫跨九龍香港區的大遊行，參與的包括胡渭康、吳嘉文、劉玉婷及徐曼華等，在雨中邊行邊高唱《為自由》。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：吳佩思  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：香港電影曾經咁講六四<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【六四專題】八九年《民主歌聲獻中華》聲援北京學運 演藝界六四自由花<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n成龍痛斥好醜好羞恥<br />\n<br />\n香港電影曾經咁講六四<br />\n成龍痛斥好醜好羞恥<br />\n【六四專題】八九年《民主歌聲獻中華》聲援北京學運演藝界六四自由花"},{"pid":"1588c3c445973d8d513490a3df9d097de1b1cb93","tid":1182498,"uid":37220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"謝志鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64dcf57bd188e56468468647c0be4365a703746f","tid":1182498,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"亞視永恒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817ec50d9a8819f9036e22307bb1cfadd325dc75","tid":1182498,"uid":23734,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T08:49:27.000Z","msg":"加拿大峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"581a09817d885dbf464d748326c4ff4d3df9b719","tid":1182498,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T09:06:44.000Z","msg":"近排愛回家唔見胡渭康嘅?"}]}